OL,5, Nearly 2,500 barristers who are        
OL,6, essential to the criminal justice      
OL,7, system in England and Wales are        
OL,8, starting industrial action over        
OL,9, concerns about legal aid funding.      
OL,11,FThey will refuse to step in at the last
OL,12,Fminute to pick up court appearances or 
OL,13,Fpreparatory work for colleagues whose  
OL,14,Fcases are over-running.                
OL,16,FIt stems from an unresolved row with   
OL,17,Fthe government over funding.           
OL,19,FThe government said the action would   
OL,20,Fmake existing backlogs worse.          
